com.microsoft.azure.webjobs.script.broker

Class JavaFunctionBroker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.webjobs.script.broker.JavaFunctionBroker

  • public class JavaFunctionBroker
extends java.lang.Object
    A broker between JAR methods and the function RPC. It can load methods using reflection, and invoke them at runtime. Thread-Safety: Multiple thread.
